{
  "stem": "3721.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they jammed them in to an area that probably 1,000 people could live comfortably.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So it was terribly, terribly [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] congested.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we-- somehow, we-- this-- we had a couple of families, non-Jewish families, who helped us bring food.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So that's how we survived till the transport was taken to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "However, I tried to organize a group.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Where did you sleep?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On the floor.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I slept on the floor in this place where I-- it's interesting that when the gendarme took me from the temple into the ghetto, I went to the-- well, it was like a family friend.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But their daughter was my father's assistant, also.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And at the beginning, I was the only one moving into their house.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because their house happened to be in within the perimeter of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then, later on, my parents moved in there, also.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "While I was there, I needed someone-- I, I was-- during the day, I was afraid to go out of the ghetto because I didn't want this guy to see me again and to know what happened to me.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I send somebody who lived in that area for my father.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because we had-- my father collected quite a-- an amount of gold.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because don't forget, they make teeth out of gold at that time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that was the value that you could purchase things with it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So I sent this boy to get some of it because I was going to purchase with that certain survival armor-- survival equipment, namely arms.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I would be able to already get that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And it so happened-- is I wound up with a revolver and a automatic handgun, two guns, and also a .22-caliber rifle with ammunition.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
